# FastAPI

.md-content .md-typeset h1 { display: none; }


FastAPI framework, high performance, easy to learn, fast to code, ready for production


---
[BOLD:Documentation]: https://fastapi.tiangolo.com
[BOLD:Source Code]: https://github.com/fastapi/fastapi
---
FastAPI is a modern, fast (high-performance), web framework for building APIs with Python based on standard Python type hints.
The key features are:
[ITALIC: [BOLD:Fast]: Very high performance, on par with [BOLD:NodeJS] and [BOLD:Go] (thanks to Starlette and Pydantic). One of the fastest Python frameworks available.
] [BOLD:Fast to code]: Increase the speed to develop features by about 200% to 300%. [ITALIC:
] [BOLD:Fewer bugs]: Reduce about 40% of human (developer) induced errors. [ITALIC:
] [BOLD:Intuitive]: Great editor support. Completion everywhere. Less time debugging.
[ITALIC: [BOLD:Easy]: Designed to be easy to use and learn. Less time reading docs.
] [BOLD:Short]: Minimize code duplication. Multiple features from each parameter declaration. Fewer bugs.
[ITALIC: [BOLD:Robust]: Get production-ready code. With automatic interactive documentation.
] [BOLD:Standards-based]: Based on (and fully compatible with) the open standards for APIs: OpenAPI (previously known as Swagger) and JSON Schema.
* estimation based on tests conducted by an internal development team, building production applications.

