## 0.87.0 (2022-11-13)
Highlights of this release:
[ITALIC: Upgraded Starlette
] Now the [CODE: TestClient] is based on HTTPX instead of Requests.
[ITALIC: There are some possible [BOLD:breaking changes] in the [CODE: TestClient] usage, but @Kludex built bump-testclient to help you automatize migrating your tests. Make sure you are using Git and that you can undo any unnecessary changes (false positive changes, etc) before using [CODE: bump-testclient].
] New WebSocketException (and docs), re-exported from Starlette.
[ITALIC: Upgraded and relaxed dependencies for package extras [CODE: all] (including new Uvicorn version), when you install [CODE: "fastapi[all]"].
] New docs about how to [BOLD:Help Maintain FastAPI].

