### Reuse [BOLD:FastAPI]'s exception handlers
If you want to use the exception along with the same default exception handlers from [BOLD:FastAPI], you can import and reuse the default exception handlers from [CODE: fastapi.exception[ITALIC:handlers]:
```python
from fastapi.exception]handlers import (
http[ITALIC:exception]handler,
request[ITALIC:validation]exception[ITALIC:handler,
)
