[BOLD:SQLModel] is built on top of SQLAlchemy and Pydantic. It was made by the same author of [BOLD:FastAPI] to be the perfect match for FastAPI applications that need to use [BOLD:SQL databases].
/// tip
You could use any other SQL or NoSQL database library you want (in some cases called "ORMs"), FastAPI doesn't force you to use anything.
